{"tid":2113220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰2020年精選金句回顧","createTime":"2020-07-18T03:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T04:40:25.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa2d292bf205ba351e150944327ee790f2e2b74","tid":2113220,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"第五位：假如今晚你身邊的朋友在熱議泛民初選結果，而不是批評政府的專制控疫措施，那是香港的可悲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3Y3B5y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3Y3B5y.png&h=d811eb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四位：房署係咪真係以為我係「泛民」？？？咁真係侮辱喎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zvwX0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zvwX0W.jpg&h=8ae56b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三位：作為一個有身份嘅人，如無必要，我一向都盡量避免與何君堯對鬧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sp6OTeM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSp6OTeM.jpg&h=1e176d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二位：我甚少談論「黃店」，而我只是想公道地反問一句：「你有想過那幾位離世子女的家人嗎？假如你有想過的話，你口中的牛（/人）肉如何嚥得下去？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTFMdJe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTFMdJe.png&h=922d0e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一位：我都係做自己嘢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Um0Jok5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUm0Jok5.png&h=d16dc9e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ff690cd032e1041a3132a4f109c8fabd8b2402f","tid":2113220,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"支持反初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c91e6376410759d57d595e19c4f73e7cbe76d3","tid":2113220,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0de4519b78c89f43e7d939fda3bca248b004b186","tid":2113220,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime